    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a recent suspension refresh using high-durometer bushings. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity matches its high-revving performance. Finished in Carbon Black, this example offers a visceral driving experience with precise steering feedback and a resonant exhaust note, making it an ideal candidate for the dedicated purist.",
